  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t民主中国国旗<br/>\n<br/>\r\n先给出个人的方案：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n1.五色旗<br/>\n<br/>\r\n含意：取自中国传统哲学概念，即金、木、水、火、土的五方色概念，白色表示金，蓝色表示木，黑色表示水，红色表示火，黄色表示土。五色同时亦代表汉、满、蒙、回、藏五族共和。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n中国第一面法定国旗，在中华民国国会表决通过的国旗，至少是当时各方势力以共和形式所选出的国旗，所以这面旗帜比较象征共和意义，至少精神方向是对的，只是好景不长，之后被国民党武力单方面改旗易帜，又到后来的共产党非法建国，中国又陷入了类似古代枪杠子出政权的循环，为了跳出这个循环，需要彻底否定武装夺权的合法性，所以，在中共倒台后，可以恢复国号中华民国，国旗恢复五色旗，以敬告世人，任何势力以武力颠覆共和政权都是可耻的，即使夺到政权也只是一时的，做不到永久的，待垮台时就会被扫入历史的垃圾堆。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTlmMjU2MDY1OTVlNjZmNTYwZDNlLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MDAwJmhlaWdodD0yNTAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99f25606595e66f560d3e.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99f25606595e66f560d3e.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/99f25606595e66f560d3e.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>五色旗；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmI3ZWUyMTJlOTM4MjkzZGYzMDgxLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MDAwJmhlaWdodD0yNTAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b7ee212e938293df3081.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b7ee212e938293df3081.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b7ee212e938293df3081.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>陆军旗（铁血十八星）；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTBiMDZlZGZkNjQ3ODk5ZjRlOTNkLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MDAwJmhlaWdodD0yNTAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50b06edfd647899f4e93d.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50b06edfd647899f4e93d.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/50b06edfd647899f4e93d.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>海军旗；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTM3ODFhNDllMzQ2YzI5NGMzY2FiLnBuZz93aWR0aD00MDAwJmhlaWdodD0yNTAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3781a49e346c294c3cab.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3781a49e346c294c3cab.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e3781a49e346c294c3cab.png?width=4000&amp;height=2500\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n空军旗；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzRkNWIzZWRlZTNiZDk3ZjkzM2M5LnBuZz93aWR0aD01MTQ2JmhlaWdodD0yNzA4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/74d5b3edee3bd97f933c9.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/74d5b3edee3bd97f933c9.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/74d5b3edee3bd97f933c9.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>中属香港旗；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmJjYWY0YTg0MWIyY2ZlOGVhZmE2LnBuZz93aWR0aD01MTQ2JmhlaWdodD0yNzA4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbcaf4a841b2cfe8eafa6.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbcaf4a841b2cfe8eafa6.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbcaf4a841b2cfe8eafa6.png?width=5146&amp;height=2708\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a>中属澳门旗；<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n参考资料：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDA2ZmYwYjZkYzJmYTQwY2YxZTQ3LnBuZz93aWR0aD01ODAmaGVpZ2h0PTUyMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/406ff0b6dc2fa40cf1e47.png?width=580&amp;height=520\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/406ff0b6dc2fa40cf1e47.png?width=580&amp;height=520\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/406ff0b6dc2fa40cf1e47.png?width=580&amp;height=520\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDI3ZDUzMTNlNjE3NjI1ZDZiMTk4LmpwZz93aWR0aD00MzImaGVpZ2h0PTcwMg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/427d5313e617625d6b198.jpg?width=432&amp;height=702\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/427d5313e617625d6b198.jpg?width=432&amp;height=702\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/427d5313e617625d6b198.jpg?width=432&amp;height=702\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGM3MjIzMTBmMTFjMWFlMzBkYWVlLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD03MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c722310f11c1ae30daee.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c722310f11c1ae30daee.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c722310f11c1ae30daee.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n <a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmM4OGVlMDdjNDc4YWE1YjdjZTM3LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNjAwJmhlaWdodD0xMjAw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc88ee07c478aa5b7ce37.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1200\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc88ee07c478aa5b7ce37.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc88ee07c478aa5b7ce37.jpg?width=1600&amp;height=1200\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
